01:38:40,559 --> 01:38:41,674
Quoi ?

1063
01:38:41,840 --> 01:38:43,831
Tu sais. cacher le livre ?

1064
01:38:49,479 --> 01:38:51,071
Oui. j‘ai...

1065
01:38:51,240 --> 01:38:53,913
Tu n'as toujours pas plus de chance
